  "steps": [
    {
      "id": "tutorial-storage-management-01",
      "markerIndex": 0,
      "replayStartSec": 2.410441,
      "replayEndSec": 12.69586,
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-storage-management/tutorial-storage-management-01.05800be7.mp3",
      "audioDurationSec": 5.146122,
      "textHash": "05800be7474114c9af193cdb81a31695d21c4e4877fadcd63f3403455ba6491a",
      "narrationText": "املأ المستودع حتى قرابة الحد ثم تحقق: نظام الملفات بدأ يضيق.",
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-storage-management/tutorial-storage-management-01-after.e4e5edf9.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 2.272653,
      "afterTextHash": "e4e5edf91ab2e59612cc697dd83ad8aa3a18f554a77fb60308e6e31a80058eb2"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-storage-management-02",
      "markerIndex": 1,
      "replayStartSec": 12.69586,
      "replayEndSec": 19.886575,
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-storage-management/tutorial-storage-management-02.869f86d4.mp3",
      "audioDurationSec": 8.437551,
      "textHash": "869f86d44259c23b6974bec0ce486de84f3cfa8dfdf913ac941c2dead3f70d42",
      "narrationText": "وسّعه وهو متصل. يكبر الحاوي المشفّر ونظام الملفات بينما تستمر الحاويات في العمل، دون أي توقف ودون أي إلغاء تحميل.",
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-storage-management/tutorial-storage-management-02-after.21fc03de.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 2.507755,
      "afterTextHash": "21fc03de90d1292b304fc9f636d6e5cf3840e68901a04ab3ad316544f4524d56"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-storage-management-03",
      "markerIndex": 2,
      "replayStartSec": 19.886575,
      "replayEndSec": 26.982758,
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-storage-management/tutorial-storage-management-03.5f7bd3fe.mp3",
      "audioDurationSec": 3.317551,
      "textHash": "5f7bd3fe3d5768cdbae54dc1f9a4597876f88a3faa7abd195d9328fae0ba50ca",
      "narrationText": "تحقّق من الداخل: نفس القرص، لكن بضعف المساحة.",
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-storage-management/tutorial-storage-management-03-after.1bbd9cca.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 1.227755,
      "afterTextHash": "1bbd9cca4e22d2e270d2223a429a60b0792b6ac46519a6f463f488a61dcca4b6"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-storage-management-04",
      "markerIndex": 3,
      "replayStartSec": 26.982758,
      "replayEndSec": 33.464064,
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-storage-management/tutorial-storage-management-04.00edc75b.mp3",
      "audioDurationSec": 10.03102,
      "textHash": "00edc75b87436fc77addf6e6c31b54feda8d9cdbb8f49a2655a9f5ff52b00f34",
      "narrationText": "الآن في الاتجاه المعاكس. احذف الملف الكبير، لكن انتبه: المجمع لا يستعيد المساحة بعد. تبقى الكتل المحذوفة محجوزة داخل الـ image.",
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-storage-management/tutorial-storage-management-04-after.3e35e73f.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 2.507755,
      "afterTextHash": "3e35e73f0102041510036cfa7e1c199e4dad1525201a712720018770f2529f7b"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-storage-management-05",
      "markerIndex": 4,
      "replayStartSec": 33.464064,
      "replayEndSec": 40.097562,
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-storage-management/tutorial-storage-management-05.edd7a861.mp3",
      "audioDurationSec": 6.19102,
      "textHash": "edd7a861b929a9e1697753a9b7fd179132b1a78833912585a093bb864ac9577b",
      "narrationText": "الـ trim يعيد تلك الكتل إلى مجمع datastore، وهو متصل. هذه هي الخطوة التي تنساها معظم الإعدادات.",
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-storage-management/tutorial-storage-management-05-after.919d91c1.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 2.429388,
      "afterTextHash": "919d91c1515e30288805b4ae69966e01b2e0857264526c5641bb3ee7aa237e74"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-storage-management-06",
      "markerIndex": 5,
      "replayStartSec": 40.097562,
      "replayEndSec": 50.538253,
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-storage-management/tutorial-storage-management-06.14e859d4.mp3",
      "audioDurationSec": 8.75102,
      "textHash": "14e859d4960e0259636a044f2f616babe0c30c24cdbf099de49500af96081862",
      "narrationText": "توقف الآن عن فعل هذا يدوياً. تُفعّل الـ policy النمو التلقائي حتى حد أقصى تختاره، إضافةً إلى عمليات trim مجدولة.",
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-storage-management/tutorial-storage-management-06-after.1816a8d3.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 2.690612,
      "afterTextHash": "1816a8d34cd9e3e0ec870a43553c5b14a65ced5c85a6ae917b50a91aceefbe1d"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-storage-management-07",
      "markerIndex": 6,
      "replayStartSec": 50.538253,
      "replayEndSec": 57.423655,
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-storage-management/tutorial-storage-management-07.5dec45f1.mp3",
      "audioDurationSec": 4.519184,
      "textHash": "5dec45f16d1ee77f174481806b882dfd8e1b76aa453da54248f6096b02bafe92",
      "narrationText": "اقرأها من جديد: النمو التلقائي مفعّل، والحد الأقصى ثمانية غيغابايت، والـ trim على جدول زمني.",
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-storage-management/tutorial-storage-management-07-after.3a400c83.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 1.880816,
      "afterTextHash": "3a400c83f7f5fcd20ca43c747cbb00018d6f4e62eebc8a54400c06e6b59662ae"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-storage-management-08",
      "markerIndex": 7,
      "replayStartSec": 57.423655,
      "replayEndSec": 63.270016,
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-storage-management/tutorial-storage-management-08.33978ee3.mp3",
      "audioDurationSec": 9.16898,
      "textHash": "33978ee327342625b608cdd9932749e47ab4a91218443ac10184bbef8819d073",
      "narrationText": "والعرض الذي يجمع كل هذا معاً: صحة التخزين تُظهر استخدام كل repo، والمجمع، وكم توفّر عليك مشاركة copy-on-write.",
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-storage-management/tutorial-storage-management-08-after.d3805f5c.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 3.63102,
      "afterTextHash": "d3805f5ca9f5d61a49bb919d91d97501dd27339a4a91ba1c434a1ada285c7b7a"
    }
  ],
  "narrationAudio": [
    {
      "id": "intro",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-storage-management/intro.3b6aa0e3.mp3",
      "textHash": "3b6aa0e30bd288e7fffdc7a4cdb669fb3f54ceece50d71e6c72b48c06cc3183f",
      "audioDurationSec": 12.355918,
      "narrationText": "مرحباً بك في الدرس التعليمي الأخير! دعنا نتأكد من أنك لن تعاني من نقص في مساحة القرص مرة أخرى. سنوسّع repository كاملاً وهو يعمل، ونعيد المساحة المحذوفة إلى الـ pool، ثم نعلّم الجهاز كيف يقوم بالأمرين تلقائياً."
    },
    {
      "id": "pool-model",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-storage-management/pool-model.73d9b344.mp3",
      "textHash": "73d9b3445dc25fbe5b06355391756f9de4ab1649fb26c3db588d43180d0729e3",
      "audioDurationSec": 19.957551,
      "narrationText": "إليك النموذج. كل repository هو ملف في datastore pool مشترك واحد. يمكن للـ repositories أن تنمو وهي تعمل بينما تستمر الـ containers في التشغيل. لكن حذف البيانات داخل الـ repo لا يحرر أي شيء بمفرده. الـ Trim هو ما يعيد الكتل إلى الـ pool. والـ policy تُؤتمت الأمرين معاً."
    },
    {
      "id": "next-tutorial",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-storage-management/next-tutorial.f416dc0a.mp3",
      "textHash": "f416dc0af0eda8029f9ab18e15453f83f67c8f8570d27fb2ac128c838e890e66",
      "audioDurationSec": 9.560816,
      "narrationText": "وهكذا نختتم السلسلة! ثمانية عشر درساً تعليمياً، من التثبيت إلى التخزين التلقائي. خوادمك أصبحت في يدك من جديد. شكراً على المشاهدة!"
    }
  ],
